Summary: Properties of the ClassScriptCreateDialog class including their types, default values, and override relationships.

dialog_hide_on_ok (bool): overrides AcceptDialog's dialog_hide_on_ok. Default: false
ok_button_text (String): overrides AcceptDialog's ok_button_text. Default: "Create"
title (String): overrides Window's title. Default: "Attach Node Script"
